data.title: Kelly Johnson - Women's Swimming and Diving
data.meta_description: Kelly JohnsonFreestyle, Butterfly  - 2008-09 (Jr.): Earned third letter at Ball State . . . clocked a season-fast time of 53.84 in the 100 free at the Mid-American
data.text:
2008-09 (Jr.): Earned third letter at Ball State . . . clocked a season-fast time of 53.84 in the 100 free at the Mid-American Conference Championships (2/25) . . . added season-best marks in the 50 free (24.83), 200 free (1:59.06), 500 free (5:20.85) and 100 fly (1:00.66) during the year . . . her 50 and 100 free times ranked sixth on the squad, while her 200 and 500 free clockings were seventh.

2007-08 (So.): Earned second letter at Ball State . . . ranked sixth on the squad in the 50 free with a 25.46 versus Toledo (11/2) . . . tallied BSU's seventh-best individual efforts in the 100 free (54.69) and 200 free (2:00.05) at Buffalo (11/10) . . . ranked ninth on the squad in the 100 fly (1:01.60).

2006-07 (Fr.): Earned first letter at Ball State . . . placed seventh in the 100 fly with a career-best clocking of 57.78 at the MAC Championships (2/14) . . . also recorded a 13th-place finish in the 50 free (24.31) and 14th-place effort in the 100 free (52.92) at the league meet . . . her prelim times of 24.18 (50 free) and 52.90 (100 free) at the league meet are career-best efforts and ranked as the first and second-best individual efforts on the team, respectively . . . also clocked a career-fast 1:58.54 in the 100 free at Miami (11/3).

HIGH SCHOOL: Earned four letters at Homestead for Coach Chad Englehart . . . holds the school record in the 50 free (23.85), 100 free (52.33), 200 free relay and the 400 free relay . . . four-year first team all-conference recipient . . . named Swimmer of the Year as a senior . . . served as team captain as a junior and senior . . . state qualifier . . . earned a sectional and conference championship in the 50 and 100 free.
